name: Cypher
description: Cypher is the market infrastructure for Ethereum Layer 1, built for and owned by its users. Liquidity is the lifeblood for capital markets, and for too long it has been controlled by misaligned actors. Cypher powers the markets where capital is raised, traded, and distributed. A complete stack of liquidity and capital formation products, combining a v4 AMM, ICO platform, permissionless launchpad, and a whole suite of tooling. The protocol is designed to support Ethereum native builders, rewarding and distributing ownership to its users.
